    "# ── PRECINCT-LEVEL EXTENSION ──────────────────────────────────────────────────\n",
    "# Load the precinct (VTD) graph.  The file must live alongside KS_vtd.json.\n",
    "# The precinct graph nodes are expected to carry the same GEOID20 attribute\n",
    "# used to join back to the shapefile later.\n",
